Name: Delete recipe
Actors: Users with accounts
Goals: Delete a recipe from the database storing all recipes
Preconditions: User must have an account and at least one saved recipe
Summary: User deletes a selected recipe and clears it from the recipe database
Related use case: Add Recipe, Edit Recipe
Steps: Actors - System Response
1. Requests to delete a recipe - 2. Asks for the user to select a recipe
3. Selects the recipe(s) to be deleted - 4. Prompt the selection of confirmation/ canceling
5. Choose confirm or cancel to delete the selected recipe(s) - 6. Confirmation of the deletion/cancellation of the selected recipe(s)
Postconditions: The selected recipe(s) should be deleted from the recipe database
